nodes.text: Gabo Tychee was a male Rodian who recently worked for Jabba Desilijic Tiure and the Hutt crime syndicate during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. After committing a terrible crime against the Hutts, his bounty was 4,000 credits alive and 2,000 dead. In 32 BBY, he was later found and captured by Jango Fett on Outland Transit Station. Prior to this, Tychee was seen with numerous affiliates at spaceports along Core trade routes.
